query:
SELECT 
  COUNT(*) as total_trades,
  SUM(CASE WHEN t.status = 'open' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as open_trades,
  SUM(CASE WHEN t.status = 'closed' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as closed_trades,
  MAX(t.createdAt) as last_created
FROM trades t
JOIN trading_accounts ta ON t.accountId = ta.id
WHERE ta.accountNumber = '163032743';
